```csharp
using Pulumi;
using AzureNextGen = Pulumi.AzureNextGen;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var token = new AzureNextGen.ContainerRegistry.V20190501Preview.Token("token", new AzureNextGen.ContainerRegistry.V20190501Preview.TokenArgs
        {
            Credentials = new AzureNextGen.ContainerRegistry.V20190501Preview.Inputs.TokenCredentialsPropertiesArgs
            {
                Certificates = 
                {
                    new AzureNextGen.ContainerRegistry.V20190501Preview.Inputs.TokenCertificateArgs
                    {
                        EncodedPemCertificate = "",
                        Name = "certificate1",
                    },
                },
            },
            RegistryName = "myRegistry",
            ResourceGroupName = "myResourceGroup",
            ScopeMapId = "/subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/resourceGroups/myResourceGroup/providers/Microsoft.ContainerRegistry/registries/myRegistry/scopeMaps/myScopeMap",
            Status = "disabled",
            TokenName = "myToken",
        });
    }

}
```

```go
package main

import (
	containerregistry "github.com/pulumi/pulumi-azure-nextgen/sdk/go/azure/containerregistry/v20190501preview"
	"github.com/pulumi/pulumi/sdk/v2/go/pulumi"
)

func main() {
	pulumi.Run(func(ctx *pulumi.Context) error {
		_, err := containerregistry.NewToken(ctx, "token", &containerregistry.TokenArgs{
			Credentials: &containerregistry.TokenCredentialsPropertiesArgs{
				Certificates: containerregistry.TokenCertificateArray{
					&containerregistry.TokenCertificateArgs{
						EncodedPemCertificate: pulumi.String(""),
						Name:                  pulumi.String("certificate1"),
					},
				},
			},
			RegistryName:      pulumi.String("myRegistry"),
			ResourceGroupName: pulumi.String("myResourceGroup"),
			ScopeMapId:        pulumi.String("/subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/resourceGroups/myResourceGroup/providers/Microsoft.ContainerRegistry/registries/myRegistry/scopeMaps/myScopeMap"),
			Status:            pulumi.String("disabled"),
			TokenName:         pulumi.String("myToken"),
		})
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		return nil
	})
}
```
